instructions: put the dinner plate in the center of the table cloth
put the salad plate on top of the dinner plate
place folded napkin in center of the salad plate
place wine glass in top right corner of table cloth
place water glass diagonally below the wine glass
place the salad fork on the bottom left of the table cloth
place the dinner fork to the right of the salad fork
place the dinner knife directly to the right of the plates
place the soup spoon to the right of the knife
